snippet.title: Order & Chaos Duels / iPhone / iPad / Android - Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Now available for free on iOS - http://gmlft.co/6nj54 - and on Android - http://gmlft.co/s8zJL!

Rediscover the Order & Chaos universe in this collectible card game. Battle with evil forces in many adventures or against real players for leaderboard supremacy!

More info coming soon on the official Order & Chaos website: http://www.orderandchaos.net/duels
